snippet.title: re:publica Portland 2019 – Amber Case: Designing Calm Technology
snippet.description:
In the age of automation, customer service and human touch will become increasingly important. Machines shouldn’t act like humans, and humans shouldn’t act like machines. How can we design technology at human scale? 

Amber Case:
https://portland.sequencer-tour.com/en/user/22336

Find out more at: https://portland.sequencer-tour.com/en/session/designing-calm-technology

(CC BY-SA 4.0 DE)
